channel.title: <@Albi> sukebei, can u NOT?
channel.description: i don't need to hear don't do it blah blah blah and all that ****, i need a straight answer, does overdosing hurt. I'm 14 years old from oshawa turning 15 in the next month, i bet your wondering why i'm asking this? well, its tuesday right now, and the thursday that just passed i had sex with my boyfriend.. we used a condom and everything and when he took the condom off the *** was still in there. but i have sharp pains in my lower stomach, and it seems like its harder to.. poop. so.. i think i might be pregnant, and i'm really scared.. if i get pregnant and go through with telling my mom, ill never be able to see or talk to my boyfriend again.. he means the world to me and i do not wanna lose him. nor do i want my parents to hate him, if i take a pregnancy test and its positive i wanna kill myself.. i don't wanna go through the consiquences. i know i should have thought of all this before i even did it, but i did it. its over and done with. and if the test comes up positive.. i need to know a painless death. i'm so scared. I know how all my friends and family and such will be upset.. but you don't understand what i will have to go through with there 15 year old daughter being pregnant.. i don't wanna go through it. just please.. does overdosing hurt? and what other deaths could i consider.. answer please.
